      "charEnd": 3474,
      "charStart": 3202,
      "factId": "hz.web.d26fad50918e18f5.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "But the community I helped to build has been <a href=\"/article/musings-gdc25/\">getting captured</a>, as evidenced by <a href=\"/article/eidas/\">EU wallet regulations</a> and ISO standards that are consolidating around the same platform gatekeepers we set out to displace.",
